mixin eSports(containerClass)
	- let games = ['cs', 'dota', 'fortnite', 'overwatch']

	div(class=containerClass)
		.my-10(class='md:my-14')
			.flex.justify-between.items-center.mb-6
				h2.text-base.font-black.italic.text-dark.uppercase(class='md:text-2xl') eSports Betting

				a.text-grizzly-dark(href='#')
					+moreBlock({ text: 'View all esport bettings' })

			p.max-w-3xl.text-base.mb-6(class='md:mb-11')
				| Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut urna ipsum sagittis auctor vitae. Facilisi urna, arcu a tincidunt. Molestie pulvinar mauris, est quis venenatis sed eu. Urna in nullam amet mi eu. Vulputate duis sit augue vel tristique ac. Molestie id gravida dolor pretium fermentum pharetra ut.
				br
				br
				| Facilisi urna, arcu a tincidunt. Molestie pulvinar mauris, est quis venenatis sed eu. Urna in nullam amet mi eu.

			.mx-auto.mt-10.flex.flex-col.gap-y-4(class='lg:mx-0 md:flex-row md:justify-between md:gap-x-6')
				each game in games
					.relative.isolate.overflow-hidden.w-full.h-28.flex.items-center.justify-center(class='md:w-64')
						img.absolute.inset-0.-z-10.h-full.w-full.object-cover.rounded-lg(
							src=require(`@/assets/images/eSports/${game}.png`),
							alt=`${game} background`,
							class='md:object-center'
						)
						img(src=require(`@/assets/images/eSports/${game}-logo.png`), alt=`${game} logo`)
